-4c27-a721-799a4c16fbf0","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"まあnodeで環境差がでちゃうからどうしようもないか、なおそう...","ts":"1589272584.010700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"l5iu"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"bf188862-c17c-4ada-b33b-472139dd39fc","type":"message","user":"U8996GYBF","text":"なんとなく分かってきた、Actionを使う側でtextlintを使ってるかも分からないんですね","ts":"1589272599.011000","edited":{"user":"U8996GYBF","ts":"1589272609.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Pyg="}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"60478c84-4fcb-4965-bdc6-5bf9f488aceb","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"です、それを込みで提供しないとActionとしてはどうなのかな感があって...\nむろん部分提供で他のActionと連携前提のもありますが","ts":"1589272638.011800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"5bR"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"d8a444d3-3b1c-46cb-8238-94ba45b0cbcc","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"まあeslintのPRは意味がないのははっきりした","ts":"1589272650.012200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"vDU"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"9a7df11b-4f86-420c-b02a-1779f8dbb655","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"(thincaさんのはdockerイメージ版の印象で勘違いしたんだな)","ts":"1589272725.013800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"+X8k="}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"20d025bd-cc26-4666-9c5f-58986a1a82bf","type":"message","user":"U8996GYBF","text":"GitHub Actionの思想がよく分かってないんですけど、使う側のリポジトリがtextlintを使っているの前提で\n- .node-versionのnodeをインストールして\n- `npm install`\n- `npm run textlint` を実行する\nくらいじゃダメなんですかね・・・？","ts":"1589272788.014900","team"